name: Westlaf Good Wood Necklaces
description:
We’ve managed to create our own “Good Wood” style necklaces. These custom engraved natural wood necklaces have either WL logo or “Laf” logo pendants (12 of each) and are only $15. The perfect accessory for any Westlaf tee!

As with all Westlaf products, the Knowledge tees include the following features:

-Exclusive design 
-Limited edition (only 12 made) 
-Custom “# out of 12” engraving on back
-30" wood bead chain

name: Checkers Tee & KNWLDG Tee
description:
We couldn't decide which design was better, so we choose to make two tees this month! The Checkers tee is arguably our cleanest design to date, and the KNWLDG tee revisits our Too Much Knowledge design to give you some extra swag for finals. Only 12 of each of these tees have been made.

As with all Westlaf products, the tees include the following features: 

-Exclusive design
-Limited edition (only 12 printed)
-Hand-numbered “# out of 12” sticker
-Premium packaging
-Screen printed on super soft 100% cotton

name: Guaranteed Fresh Tee & V-Neck - Yellow
description:
Announcing the first ever Westlaf V-Necks! Our much-anticipated "Guaranteed Fresh" design is available in both V-Necks and regular tees. Now on softer T-shirts (as soft as American Apparel) with tear-away tags.

As with all Westlaf products, the tees include the following features: 

-Exclusive design
-Limited edition (only 12 printed)
-Hand-numbered “# out of 12” sticker
-Premium packaging
-Screen printed on 100% cotton

name: WL Hands Tee - Green
description:
One of our most popular designs! Features a pair of hands reppin’ Westlaf, outlined in yellow on a forest green shirt.

As with all Westlaf products, the WL Diag tees include the following features:

-Exclusive design 
-Limited edition (only 24 printed) 
-Hand-numbered “# out of 24” sticker 
-Premium packaging 
-Screen printed on 100% cotton
-Westlaf Custom Wallpaper

name: WL Diag Tee - Teal
description:
As chosen by you, our latest design features a white Westlaf logo splashed diagonally on the side of a fresh, crispy teal T-shirt.

As with all Westlaf products, the WL Diag tees include the following features:
